name: Sensor Web Server Helgoland API v3.4.3
body:
Available in [Maven Central](https://search.maven.org/search?q=g:org.n52.sensorweb-server.helgoland%20and%20v:3.4.3).

## Change Log 
* None

## Dependency Updates
* Bump spotbugs-annotations from 4.4.2 to 4.7.1 (#629, #637, #638, #642, #654, #667, #679)
* Bump arctic-sea.version from 9.1.1 to 9.6.0 (#630, #636, #646, #647, #648, #662, #664, #666)
* Bump geotools.version from 26.0 to 27.0 (#631, #645, #650, #660, #674)
* Bump spring-boot-dependencies from 2.5.6 to 2.7.1 (#632, #633, #635, #640, #644, #651, #656, #659, #663, #673, #678)
* Bump junit-bom from 5.8.1 to 5.8.2 (#634)
* Bump jackson-bom from 2.13.0 to 2.13.3 (#639,  #653, #658, #668)
* Bump nokogiri from 1.12.5 to 1.13.4 (#652, #661)
* Bump indriya from 2.1.2 to 2.1.3 (#649)
* Bump joda-time from 2.10.13 to 2.10.14 (#655)
* Bump parent from 21 to 24 (#608, #665)
* Bump nokogiri from 1.13.4 to 1.13.6 in /web-resources/src/main/docs (#672)
* Bump maven-enforcer-plugin from 3.0.0 to 3.1.0 (#676)
* Bump jts-core from 1.18.2 to 1.19.0 (#677)

## Breaking Changes
* None

See [here](https://github.com/52North/sensorweb-server-helgoland/compare/v3.4.2...v3.4.3) for the complete commit log.
